name: Jose Santos
description:
I am independent man who has my own busy life, I am a man of substance and presence, wise, open and kind, family is important to me.
I want Someone calm both inside and outside, honest, loving, caring, trustworthy, hardworking, God fearing, kind, romantic, passionate, kid loving, generous and respect. Some one who I have trust, honesty and faith in her… I want someone to love me for me and me alone and not love me for what I do for them cause I give it all when it comes to a relationship and always there for my man, if he does this, I will treat him like no woman as ever I treated him and make him my one and only Love.
